{"tid":1477902,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，我地真係無得再輸了，今晚見！","createTime":"2019-08-16T09:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T09:57:47.000Z","uid":75267,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"24dd13fe934139f14948ef5a0b56ddf8c3d31793","tid":1477902,"uid":75267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:36:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jC-KG3nUGjs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjC-KG3nUGjs&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjalx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=6a1df98c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jC-KG3nUGjs</a><br />\n睇一次喊一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【「英美港盟 主權在民」集會 | Stand with Hong Kong, Power to the People Rally】<br />\n<br />\n香港大專學界事務代表團聯同「我要攬炒」團隊於8月16日星期五於中環遮打花園舉辦之「英美港盟 主權在民」集會已正式獲警方批出不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n「英美港盟 主權在民」晚會詳情如下：<br />\n日期：8月16日 星期五<br />\n時間：晚上8時正<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n<br />\n我們誠邀各位香港人出席是次晚會，與我們一起攜手突破困局。<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;Stand with Hong Kong, Power to the People&rsquo; Rally co-organized by the Hong Kong Higher Institutions International Affairs Delegation and the Stand with Hong Kong Task Force has already been approved with a notice of no objection.<br />\n<br />\nThe details of the Rally are as follows:<br />\n<br />\nDate: 16th August (Fri)<br />\nTime: 20:00<br />\nVenue: Chater Garden, Central<br />\n<br />\nWe hereby invite all Hongkongers to come and join us in overcoming our current stalemate."},{"pid":"5d7f8a293926372988e21111ae78a3d8c3fc7011","tid":1477902,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:36:31.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"439c75eff8e811a8ef739e2743ac74e6e6802890","tid":1477902,"uid":261530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-1